msgid "Speech to text"
msgstr "Spraak naar tekst"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:29
msgid ""
"Speech to text doesn't work with version 21.04.2 due to `Vosk API <"
"https://"
"github.com/alphacep/vosk-api>`_ issues. Use version 21.04.1 or 21.04.3"
" and "
"later versions."
msgstr ""
"Spraak naar tekst werkt niet met versie 21.04.2 vanwege problemen met"
" `Vosk "
"API <https://github.com/alphacep/vosk-api>`_. Gebruik versie 21.04.1 of "
"21.04.3 en latere versies."

